  29 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> konatu-20121218.ebuild:
  media-fonts/*: fix ${DOCS} to change array to list

   Because font.eclass doesn't support ${DOCS} as array,
  they are fixed to space delimited lists.

   FYI: https://devmanual.gentoo.org/eclass-reference/font.eclass/index.html

  25 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> konatu-20121218.ebuild:
  media-fonts/*: Add "mirror" to ${RESTRICT}

   Because they are not uploaded in GENTOO_MIRRORS.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> konatu-20121218.ebuild:
  Trivial fixes for QA.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml:
  Fix metadata.xml(s)

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> konatu-20121218.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

  30 May 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> konatu-20121218.ebuild:
  Update to EAPI=5 and git-r3.eclass

*konatu-20121218 (27 Jan 2015)

  27 Jan 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +konatu-20121218.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
